text: Hello Guian. Have you found somewhere. So pleased that you got into the course you wanted :slightly_smiling_face:.  How are you getting on with your project?  How are you feeling about living away from home?  I was 17 when I went to University.  It was a little daunting, but I had such a good time.  It’s quite an adjustment to have to manage everything yourself - from rent, bills, dishes and washing to taking accountability for turning up to uni and doing your work.
Hi and yes my accomodation is sorted now,thank you I can't wait to start my course. I'm excited to go to uni and live away from home but I am also a bit nervous but yeah mostly excited.
